headline.main: Lorena Ochoa to Play Her LPGA Tour Event in May
headline.print_headline: Lorena Ochoa to Play Her LPGA Tour Event in May

lead_paragraph: Lorena Ochoa is returning to LPGA Tour competition for the first time in five years, but only for her tournament.
